      <div class="card"><h3>Sound effects 🔊</h3><p style="margin:0 0 12px">Little dings on wins and level-ups.</p><button class="btn btn--g btn--sm" id="sndToggle">Sound: On</button></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Start over</h3><p style="margin:0 0 12px">Re-run the welcome setup (your progress stays).</p><button class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" id="replayOnb">Replay welcome ↺</button></div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel" data-p="help">
      <h1>The rules &amp; help</h1>
      <div class="card"><h3>The cheap-dopamine fast</h3>
